<%!-- Hero Section --%>
<section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden pt-16">
  <%!-- Background gradient --%>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-base-300 via-base-100 to-base-200"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/4 -left-32 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 -right-32 w-96 h-96 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-20">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-8">
      <.icon name="hero-information-circle-solid" class="size-4" />
      <span>Our Story</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black tracking-tight leading-tight">
      About <span class="text-primary">FitConnex</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg sm:text-xl text-base-content/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Revolutionizing the fitness industry by connecting gyms, trainers, and members in one seamless platform.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<%!-- Mission & Vision Section --%>
<section class="py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <%!-- Mission --%>
      <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-primary/10 border border-primary/20 p-8">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <.icon name="hero-rocket-launch-solid" class="size-8 text-primary" />
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          To empower fitness professionals and gym operators with innovative technology that streamlines operations,
          enhances member experiences, and drives business growth while making fitness accessible to everyone.
        </p>
      </div>

      <%!-- Vision --%>
      <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/5 to-secondary/10 border border-secondary/20 p-8">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <.icon name="hero-eye-solid" class="size-8 text-secondary" />
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-4">Our Vision</h2>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          To become the world's leading fitness ecosystem, creating a connected community where gyms thrive,
          trainers excel, and members achieve their health and wellness goals through personalized experiences.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%!-- Our Story Section --%>
<section class="py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-base-200/50">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black tracking-tight mb-6">
        How It All <span class="text-primary">Started</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        FitConnex was born from a simple observation: the fitness industry needed a unified platform that could
        bring together gym operators, trainers, and members in a meaningful way. We saw gym owners struggling with
        outdated management systems, trainers juggling multiple tools, and members searching for the right fitness
        partner without proper guidance.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-base-content/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        In 2024, our founding team—a group of fitness enthusiasts, gym operators, and technology experts—came
        together with a shared vision: to build a comprehensive ecosystem that addresses every pain point in the
        fitness journey.
      </p>
      <p>
        Today, FitConnex serves hundreds of gyms, thousands of trainers, and tens of thousands of members across
        the region. We've automated gym management, simplified trainer-client relationships, and made discovering
        the perfect gym as easy as a few clicks.
      </p>
      <p>
        But we're just getting started. Our platform continues to evolve with new features, integrations, and
        innovations that keep us at the forefront of fitness technology.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%!-- Core Values Section --%>
<section class="py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black tracking-tight">
        Our Core <span class="text-primary">Values</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <%!-- Value 1 --%>
      <div class="card bg-base-100 border border-base-300/50 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <.icon name="hero-heart-solid" class="size-6 text-primary" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Member-Centric</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/60 leading-relaxed">
          Every decision we make prioritizes the needs and experiences of our users—from gym operators to members.
