          <.icon name="hero-light-bulb-solid" class="size-6 text-secondary" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Innovation</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/60 leading-relaxed">
          We continuously push boundaries with cutting-edge technology to solve real fitness industry challenges.
        </p>
