      <%!-- Value 3 --%>
      <div class="card bg-base-100 border border-base-300/50 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <.icon name="hero-shield-check-solid" class="size-6 text-accent" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Integrity</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/60 leading-relaxed">
          We operate with transparency, honesty, and reliability in everything we do for our community.
        </p>
      </div>

      <%!-- Value 4 --%>
      <div class="card bg-base-100 border border-base-300/50 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-success/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <.icon name="hero-users-solid" class="size-6 text-success" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Community</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/60 leading-relaxed">
          We believe in building strong connections and fostering a supportive fitness ecosystem for all.
        </p>
      </div>

      <%!-- Value 5 --%>
      <div class="card bg-base-100 border border-base-300/50 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-warning/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <.icon name="hero-chart-bar-square-solid" class="size-6 text-warning" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Excellence</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/60 leading-relaxed">
          We strive for the highest quality in our platform, support, and service delivery every single day.
        </p>
      </div>

      <%!-- Value 6 --%>
      <div class="card bg-base-100 border border-base-300/50 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-info/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <.icon name="hero-bolt-solid" class="size-6 text-info" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Agility</h3>
        <p class="text-base-content/60 leading-relaxed">
          We adapt quickly to industry changes and user feedback, continuously evolving our platform.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%!-- Team Section --%>
<section class="py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-base-200/50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
